column5: Beautiful Piney Woods TX Area Lakehouse, 2600 square feet, 3-4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, extra beds to sleep 8-14, lots of yard, fenced areas for small children & outside (only) animals. Lake Winnsboro is great for swimming, boating, skiing,& fishing and is very quiet. Winnsboro is a quaint and artsy and friendly town!
column8: RHEMA Lakeside Retreat Center @ Lake Winnsboro
